item.title: CVE-2023-38563|2023-09-06T09:24:08.253Z -- tp-link -- archer%20c1200
item.description: Archer C1200 firmware versions prior to 'Archer C1200(JP)_V2_230508' and Archer C9 firmware versions prior to 'Archer C9(JP)_V3_230508' allow a network-adjacent unauthenticated attacker to execute arbitrary OS commands.
